{"title":"Maven连接Eclipse，发布第一个测试项目","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.017Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Maven连接Eclipse，发布第一个测试项目","updated":"2023-07-28T08:52:25.785Z","content":"<h2 id=\"maven连接eclipse\">Maven连接Eclipse<a title=\"#maven连接eclipse\" href=\"#maven连接eclipse\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>1、首先要配置Maven本机的环境，没有配置的可以<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105218552\" target=\"_blank\">参考这里</a><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105218552\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105218552</a></strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401160406585.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>2、进入Eclipse<br>\n——&gt;点击最上面的window，选择Preferences<br>\n——&gt;找到Maven，点击Installations<br>\n——&gt;点击右边的add<br>\n——&gt;点击Directory,选择你Maven安装的目录（不用点进去即可）<br>\n——&gt;finish<br>\n——&gt;此时会出现你新添加的Maven程序，勾选即可<br>\n——&gt;点击apply</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401160824432.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401160857952.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>3、下面配置Maven的settings.xml文件<br>\n——&gt;在Maven安装目录下面找到\\apache-maven-3.6.3\\conf\\settings.xml<br>\n——&gt;编辑内容，找到localRepository标签，设置依赖地址（地址设置你想要放的地址，我这里在Maven目录下新建了一个文件夹）<br>\n——&gt;配置mirrors，这里配置的是阿里云的mirror<br>\n——&gt;保存</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162114256.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401161529142.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401161538622.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><strong>4、在刚刚Eclipse中配置Maven的地方，选择user settings<br>\n——&gt;点击Browser,找到你settings.xml文件,添加进来<br>\n——&gt;apply</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401161941166.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>5、点击上面window<br>\n——&gt;选择show view<br>\n——&gt;选择other<br>\n——&gt;添加Maven Repository<br>\n——&gt;在下面即可看到你配置的本地仓库地址和mirror信息</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162458666.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162514796.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>6、此时Maven已经基本配置成功，可以来新建一个项目看看</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162638568.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162653523.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162704898.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401162718823.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>7、此时项目可能会报错，我们把项目所需的运行环境加进来<br>\n——&gt;右键项目，选择buildpath<br>\n——&gt;config buildpath<br>\n——&gt;选择上面的Libraries栏目<br>\n——&gt;点击右侧add library<br>\n——&gt;选择server runtime<br>\n——&gt;选择tomcat<br>\n——&gt;确定</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163225878.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163324658.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>8、jre system library也可以选择添加一下<br>\n——&gt;点击右侧add library<br>\n——&gt;选择jre system library<br>\n——&gt;选择你的jdk<br>\n——&gt;添加即可</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163534225.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163545447.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202004011638381.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>9、下面可以在tomcat中添加你的maven项目了（刚刚建的是test，我这里添加的是helloworld测试项目，其实一样的）<br>\n——&gt;启动tomcat<br>\n——&gt;在浏览器里输入项目地址就能运行啦！</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163625237.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401163749674.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Maven环境的安装","link":"2023/07/28/Maven环境的安装"},"next":{"title":"Mysql8.0开启远程访问","link":"2023/07/28/Mysql8.0开启远程访问"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Maven连接Eclipse，发布第一个测试项目/","toc":[{"id":"maven连接eclipse","title":"Maven连接Eclipse","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"968 字约 6 分钟"}